# HR Data Analytics – Presence Insights Dashboard

## 📊 Project Overview
A data-driven project to analyze employee **Presence Insights** and streamline HR operations using **Power BI** and **Excel**. The goal was to empower the HR team with real-time visibility into working hours, attendance, performance trends, and leave patterns—leading to better decision-making and operational efficiency.

---

## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
- **Power BI** – for building interactive dashboards
- **Microsoft Excel** – for data cleaning and initial exploration

---

## 📌 Key Objectives
- Analyze **employee presence patterns** (working hours, attendance, leaves)
- Identify **performance trends** and productivity-impacting behaviors
- Centralize HR data in a **single dashboard** for easy access
- Reduce manual HR tracking effort and improve daily efficiency

---

## 🔍 Features of the Dashboard
- **Attendance Analysis**: Track daily/weekly presence, late logins, and absences
- **Working Hours Overview**: Monitor total hours logged per employee or department
- **Leave Tracker**: Visualize leave distribution by type and frequency
- **Performance Summary**: Correlate presence with team/individual performance
- **Custom Filters**: Department-wise and time-period-based filtering for focused insights

---

## ⏱️ Outcome
- Estimated to **save 3–4 hours** of manual HR work daily
- Enhanced visibility into presence-related trends and outliers
- Improved data-driven decision-making for HR teams

---
